# PID controller step.
*pid(setpoint as i64, measured as i64, integral as i64, prev_err as i64, kp as i64, ki as i64, kd as i64) returns i64
    err is setpoint - measured
    derivative is err - prev_err
    kp * err + ki * (integral + err) + kd * derivative

*main
    log pid(100, 80, 5, 18, 2, 1, 1)
